sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant App as app.js入口
    participant OB as OnboardingFlow
    participant LS as localStorage
    participant ES as EmptyStateRenderer
    participant Api as ApiClient
    participant Server as Express

    Note over User,Server: 用户首次访问
    App->>LS: localStorage.getItem('onboarding_completed')
    LS-->>App: null (未完成)
    App->>OB: start()
    OB->>OB: renderStep(1) — "日摊成本是什么？"
    OB->>User: 显示概念解释modal

    User->>OB: 点击"下一步"
    OB->>LS: localStorage.setItem('onboarding_step', 2)
    OB->>OB: renderStep(2) — "添加第一件物品"
    OB->>User: 显示添加记录表单modal

    User->>OB: 填写物品信息+点击"添加"
    OB->>Api: POST /api/records {item_name, price, purchase_date}
    Api->>Server: request with JWT + CSRF
    Server-->>Api: {id: 123}
    Api-->>OB: record created
    OB->>OB: nextStep() → step 3

    OB->>OB: renderStep(3) — "探索统计视图"
    OB->>User: 显示统计Tab引导

    User->>OB: 点击"完成"
    OB->>LS: localStorage.setItem('onboarding_completed', 'true')
    OB->>ES: hide all empty states for this session
